Arduino LED commander 
---------------------

Arduino LED commander is a simple GUI for controlling an output pin of the
Arduino. This project was made as a little tutorial to show the possibility
of controlling an Arduino board with Python and a GTK interface.

Requirements
------------

- Python and Glade
- Arduino Uno http://arduino.cc/
- pyserial http://pyserial.sourceforge.net/

Download
--------

Home:   http://www.affolter-engineering.ch/index.php?page=led-commander
Git:    https://gitorious.org/arduino-led
 
